sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude/ChatGPT)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Edge
    participant MCP as RHOAI MCP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant NN as Neural Navigator<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8080/8443 TCP<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Agent,MCP: Flow 1: AI Agent Tool Invocation (e.g., list workbenches)
    Agent->>Route: MCP Request (SSE/streamable-http)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Route->>MCP: Forward (TLS terminated)<br/>HTTP/8000
    MCP->>K8s: GET /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/6443, SA Token
    K8s-->>MCP: Notebook CR List
    MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result (JSON)
    Route-->>Agent: HTTPS Response

    Note over Agent,NN: Flow 2: Neural Navigator Model Recommendation
    Agent->>Route: recommend_model tool call
    Route->>MCP: Forward HTTP/8000
    MCP->>NN: POST /api/recommend<br/>HTTP/8000 (in-cluster, no TLS)
    NN-->>MCP: Ranked Recommendations
    MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result
    Route-->>Agent: Recommendations

    Note over MCP,MR: Flow 3: Model Registry Access (Out-of-Cluster)
    Agent->>Route: list_registered_models tool call
    Route->>MCP: Forward HTTP/8000
    MCP->>MCP: Start oc port-forward tunnel
    MCP->>MR: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token (OAuth)
    MR-->>MCP: Model List
    MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result
    Route-->>Agent: Models

    Note over MCP,GH: Flow 4: Quickstart Deployment
    Agent->>Route: deploy_quickstart tool call
    Route->>MCP: Forward HTTP/8000
    MCP->>GH: git clone (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+, GIT_TERMINAL_PROMPT=0
    GH-->>MCP: Repository
    MCP->>K8s: helm install / oc apply<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8s-->>MCP: Deployment Result
    MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result
    Route-->>Agent: Deployment Status
